Class Potato

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.carleton.sysc3110.project.models.BoardElement
      • ca.carleton.sysc3110.project.models.plants.Plant
        • ca.carleton.sysc3110.project.models.plants.Potato
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BoardElement>

    public class Potato
extends Plant
    The Class SeedSpitter. The SeedSpitter is the basic attack unit for the plants. It takes up one tile of space and period fires a SEED bullet. It is on a two turn cooldown and requires 75 sun points to purchase.
    Author:
    John Blackwood , Nikola Neskovic
